=head1 History revision for DiCoP

This document details the complete changes from v3.01 onwards.

v3.00 was seperated from Dicop-Server and is the first real, working version.

=head2 2006-05-02 (Proxy v3.02)

No functional changes:

=over 2

=item fixed

	Makefile.PL: use YAML to generate better META.yml
		     use PREREQ_FATAL
		     need Linux::Cpuinfo are prereq
	fix (c) dates, contact address etc
	make a non-beta version for release
	add a SIGNATURE again (for CPAN release)
	wcr lib: Total: lines 685, words 2225, chars 16848
	33 tests

=back

